# MSH Management System — Cursor Rules

## Project Overview
MySecondHome (MSH) is a premium pet boarding facility management system in Dubai.
Staff-facing admin tool. Not client-facing.

## Tech Stack
- Frontend: React + TypeScript + Vite
- UI: shadcn/ui + Tailwind CSS
- Database: Supabase (PostgreSQL)
- State/Data: @tanstack/react-query
- Routing: React Router

## Critical File Paths
- Supabase client: `src/integrations/supabase/client.ts`
- Supabase types: `src/integrations/supabase/types.ts` (NOT src/types/database.types.ts)
- Env variable for anon key: `VITE_SUPABASE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY` (NOT VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY)
- Dev server runs on: `localhost:8080` (NOT 5173)
- Project ID: `pfrbeiwqbjcexwjfekwn`

## Existing Hooks (always import from these, never recreate)
- `src/hooks/useOwners.ts` — useOwners(searchTerm?), useOwner(id), useCreateOwner(), useUpdateOwner()
- `src/hooks/usePets.ts` — usePets(ownerId), usePet(id), useCreatePet(), useUpdatePet(), getVaccinationStatus()
- `src/hooks/useBookings.ts` — useBookings(start,end), useRooms(), useCreateBooking(), useCheckIn(), useCheckOut()
- `src/hooks/useWallet.ts` — useWalletTransactions(ownerId), useTopUpWallet(), useDeductWallet()
- `src/hooks/useDaycare.ts` — useDaycarePackages(), useDaycarePackage(), useCreateDaycarePackage(), useAddDaycareDay(), useMarkSessionAttended(), useDeleteDaycareSession()
- `src/hooks/usePark.ts` — useParkBookings(date), useParkDayFlag(date), useCreateParkBooking(), useDeleteParkBooking(), useSetParkDayFlag()
- `src/hooks/useGrooming.ts` — useGroomingAppointments(date), useGroomingHistory(petId), useCreateGroomingAppointment(), useUpdateGroomingAppointment(), useMarkInProgress/Complete/NoShow(), useBookingsForGroomingLink()
- `src/lib/bookingUtils.ts` — calculateNights(), formatBookingCell(), getStatusColour(), isBookingOnDate(), generateDateRange()

## Database Tables (key ones)
- owners: id, first_name, last_name, phone, email, member_type, wallet_balance, is_vip, always_same_room, camera_required
- pets: id, owner_id, name, species, breed, date_of_birth, weight_kg, gender, spayed_neutered, assessment_status
- vaccinations: id, pet_id, vaccine_name, expiry_date, administered_date
- rooms: id, wing, display_name, room_type, capacity_type, max_pets, is_active, cam_number
- bookings: id, booking_ref, owner_id, room_id, check_in_date, check_out_date, status, do_not_move
- booking_pets: id, booking_id, pet_id
- booking_addons: id, booking_id, addon_type, description, unit_price
- wallet_transactions: id, owner_id, transaction_type, amount, balance_after, payment_method
- invoices: id, invoice_number, owner_id, booking_id, status, total
- daycare_packages: id, owner_id, pet_id, total_days, days_used, purchase_date
- daycare_sessions: id, owner_id, pet_id, package_id, session_date, checked_in, pickup_used, dropoff_used, logged_by, notes
- park_bookings: id, visit_date, slot_start, slot_end, size_lane, owner_id, pet_id
- park_day_flags: id, visit_date, status (open/closed/assessment_only), notes
- grooming_appointments: id, owner_id, pet_id, booking_id, service, appointment_date, appointment_time, duration_minutes, price, status, visit_notes, no_show
- staff: id, first_name, last_name, role, email, active

## Room Wings
- oxford (Oxford Street — 8 rooms, Presidential Suites)
- piccadilly (Piccadilly — 7 rooms, Royal Suites)
- park_lane (Park Lane — 4 rooms, Royal Suites)
- fleet (Fleet Street — 6 rooms, Double/Single Royal)
- back_kennels (Back Kennels — 7 rooms, mixed)
- cattery (25 rooms — Super Presidential x5, Presidential x8, Deluxe x12)
- grooming_upstairs (1 room)

## Booking Reference Format
Auto-generated by DB trigger: MSH-2026-00001

## Business Rules
- Park: 10 slots per day (08:00-17:00), each slot has Small Dog + Big Dog lane, 1 booking per lane
- Daycare: sold as 12-day packages, sessions consume credits
- Boarding: room conflict detection handled by DB trigger
- Wallet: balance auto-synced by DB trigger after each transaction
- Member types: standard / silver / gold

## Code Conventions
- Always use @tanstack/react-query for data fetching — never raw fetch/useEffect for DB calls
- Always invalidate relevant query cache after mutations
- Use shadcn/ui components — never raw HTML form elements
- Status colour coding: confirmed=blue, checked_in=green, checked_out=grey, enquiry=yellow, cancelled=red
- Currency always displayed as "AED X,XXX.XX"
- Dates displayed as "5 Apr 2026" format where possible
- Never create new Supabase tables — schema is fixed
- Never use VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY — use VITE_SUPABASE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY

